                        <note rend="inline" type="source">723.2515/3283: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-03-12T13:00:00-05:00">March 12, 1929—1
                                p.m.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>24. Please give Minister for Foreign Affairs copy of Ambassador Moore’s
                            cable to me No. 28, March 11, 5 p.m., which was repeated to you.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi></signed></closer>
